\cf1\b\i Program Runner\cf0\i0  \b0 is an utility that helps you to run any external program, without write any Code!!\line By just 1 click, \cf1\b\i Program Runner\i0   \cf0\b0 creates a proper dedicated script, that fires-up the program you wanted. Any!! From Word to Excel, to Chrome, to MP3TAG, to DDP_to_CUE, to any ...\par
